title: Easyprint Printer Paper and Copier Paper 10,000 Sheets 20 x 500 A4 Premium Brilliant White CIE 160 Test Winner PEFC Environmental Certificate
features: Our high-quality Easyprint printer paper and copy paper is the ideal choice for all your printing and copying needs, whether at home or in the office.
With its high whiteness (CIE 160), it ensures crisp prints and clear copies.
Quantity: 10,000 sheets = 20 packs of 500 sheets | Thickness: 103 μm | Opacity: 94% | Smoothness: 28s | Premium White (CIE 160)
Our Easyprint printer paper and copy paper is made from sustainably managed forests and is awarded the PEFC certificate (GFA-PEFC-COC-500582).
Thanks to the high opacity of our A4 copy paper, our printer paper prevents texts and images from showing through on the back of the letterboard.
description: Product Description Discover Easyprint printer and copier paper Discover our range of A4 printer and copier paper – ideal for all your printing and copying needs. Whether you need small quantities like 500, 1,500 or 2,500 sheets for your home office, or larger quantities like 5,000 sheets for the workplace – our Easyprint printer and copier paper is available in the right pack size. We offer A4 copier paper without compromising on quality. Easyprint printer and copier paper A4 is perfect for everyday use and stands out in product comparisons – especially in terms of thickness and whiteness. Best of all: Easyprint printer and copier paper is PEFC certified, so you can print and copy with a clear conscience. Certified by PEFC Germany e.V. in 2023 (PEFC/04-31-3684) Your benefits at a glance Printer paper Regardless of the brand or type of printer you use: Our printer paper is perfect for all common office and home office printers. Copier Paper Our high-quality A4 copier paper is compatible with a wide range of common copiers and consistently delivers clear and reliable copies, regardless of manufacturer or device model. 500 to 150,000 sheets Our high-quality printer and copier paper is available in 500, 1,500, 2,500, 5,000, 10,000, 20,000, 25,000, 35,000, 70,000, 140,000 and 150,000 sheets to meet your paper needs for a variety of projects. A4 format A4 printer and copier paper is highly versatile, suitable for everything from professional documents to everyday notes – a practical standard. High opacity With an ideal balance between weight and strength, our A4 printer and copier paper delivers outstanding results. The result: razor-sharp print quality thanks to high opacity. Whiteness CIE 160 An exceptionally high degree of whiteness ensures razor-sharp print results and presents text as well as graphics with impressive clarity and brilliance.
